{"tid":2385197,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3次分區檢驗來嘅經驗","createTime":"2021-01-29T02:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T10:20:05.000Z","uid":374427,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"13de2459bc873666fd52c698d134edf4c9abdc20","tid":2385197,"uid":374427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T02:01:32.000Z","msg":"喺呢2/3次嘅 &ldquo;突擊&ldquo; 封區過程，佢地都有大同小異嘅現象：<br />\n1. 果一帶多感染個案<br />\n2. 放工時間封區（兩次突擊都係7點）<br />\n3. 半夜開返區<br />\n4. 行動前多狗車聚集、起大量帳蓬、白衫檢驗人員遊盪<br />\n5. 狗駐守封鎖線<br />\n6. 有膠管落區視察冇人嘅街道<br />\n<br />\n所以如果唔想比人撩喉嚨，就要：<br />\n1. 見狗/白衣人帳蓬就報哨<br />\n  （尤其係有狗從狗車上面落地）<br />\n2. 執定逃生包（有水、儲糧、日用品、錢...）<br />\n     － 隨時走人<br />\n3. 平日記得拉窗簾，費事封左先拉咁明顯，或者直接見到單位內有冇人<br />\n4. 意識到自己喺封鎖線內，講野就細聲d，動作都唔好咁大<br />\n（3＆4 如果唔係會比人知道單位入面有人）<br />\n<del>5. 遲放工（呢兩次都係夜晚7點封）</del><br />\n<br />\n記住，佢一日未講封區大家一日都可以自由進出果個區域！<br />\n<br />\n同埋，如果你相信檢查嘅，撩完唔代表免疫，預防感染措施一樣要做好。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">政府你肯封關未？</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zJoGW5v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzJoGW5v.jpg&h=1ad05525&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9fb08442d35b6891c2e1fa74a41ebd114c9f7cb3","tid":2385197,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T06:13:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7c0a68a50b52b2e51c4b69ed63f8b8b80c5425","tid":2385197,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:01:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c90